Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 07:28:51 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Exp 3: TermSurf dock AppIcon padding (~10% side inset)

Regenerate TermSurf.appiconset and AppIconImage from factory dock master
with dock_content_scale=0.89 so the mark sits at ~80% plate width with
~10% left/right navy padding (Issue 26072011262273).
